wiki.summary: "In the Morning" (stylized in sentence case, also called "Mafia in the Morning") is a song recorded by South Korean girl group Itzy. It was released on April 30, 2021, through JYP Entertainment, as the lead single from the group's fourth extended play, Guess Who. Produced by JYP Entertainment's founder, J.Y. Park, alongside South Korean songwriters Danke and Kass and composer Lee Hae-sol, the track's transfixing chorus sees the group explore various new vocal styles to match the trippy synth of the single. Read more on Last.fm.
